</div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12  col-xs-12 bs zoom" id="started"
      style="margin-top:20px;float:left;position:relative;padding-left:20px;" role="alert">
      <h3 style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-thickness:10%;">How it actually started?</h3>
      <p>Several of the early cases had visited Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market and so the virus is thought to have a
        zoonotic origin.The virus that caused the outbreak is known as SARS‑CoV‑2, a newly discovered virus closely
        related to bat coronaviruses,pangolin coronaviruses,and SARS-CoV.The scientific consensus is that COVID-19 has a
        natural origin.The probable bat-to-human infection may have been among people processing bat carcasses and guano
        in the production of traditional Chinese medicines.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
      <img id="cimg" src="https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JtVH5Khvihib7dBDFY9ZDR.jpg" alt="network error">
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4  col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 bs zoom" id="symptoms" style="color:#303960;" role="alert">
      <h3 style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-thickness:10%;">Symptoms to be noted:</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left:15px;">
        <li>Fever or Chills</li>
        <li>Cough</li>
        <li>Fatigue</li>
        <li>Headache</li>
        <li>Sore throat</li>
        <li>Congestion or runny nose</li>
        <li>Diarrhea</li>
        <li>Muscle or body aches</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bs zoom col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12" id="precautions">
  <img src="images/precautions.gif" style="height:60px;width:60px;">
  <h2 style="text-align:left;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-thickness:10%;">Precautions</h2>
  <ol style="text-align:left;margin-left:10px;">
    <li>Stay Home and Maintain Social Distance</li>
    <li>Wash Hands Often</li>
    <li>Cover your cough</li>
    <li>Wear a Mask when out</li>
    <li>Sick?Call a helpline</li>
  </ol>
</div>

<div class='jumbotron row col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 world'>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <h1>Total Confirmed</h1>
    <h4><%= TConfirmed %> </h4>
    <h1>New Confirmed</h1>
    <h4><%=Newconfirmed%></h4>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <h1>Total Deaths </h1>
    <h4><%= TDeaths %></h4>
    <h1>New Deaths</h1>
    <h4><%=Newdeaths%></h4>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <h1>Total Recovered</h1>
    <h4><%= TRecovered %></h4>
    <h1>New Recovered</h1>
    <h4><%= Newrecovered%></h4>
  </div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript">

  var count = 0;

    var ctx = document.getElementById('myChart1').getContext('2d');

    Chart.defaults.global.defaultFontSize = 18;
